  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Build a Humanist school in Mbarara District-Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will build an extension class room at Reason Foundation School to enable us enhance and extend affordable but yet quality secular education for children-at-risk and orphans, from poor families and those with special needs in Mbarara District south western Uganda. The the classroom structure will provide study space/shelter to 50 extra children to attend class in a conducive environment. currently we have limited space and yet we would love to accommodate more children.</narrative>
  </description>
